nija-bot/
│
├─ .env                  # Your environment variables
├─ main.py               # Entry point (script I just gave you)
├─ nija_client.py        # CoinbaseClient class (with debug, fetch accounts)
├─ requirements.txt      # Python dependencies (requests, loguru, python-dotenv)
├─ README.md             # Instructions for running the bot
└─ logs/                 # Optional folder if you want to store logs
